<li>容器 div 需要指定宽高</li>
</ul>
<p>其余用法与 html 中编码无异</p>
<h2 id="百度地图组件封装" tabindex="-1">百度地图组件封装</h2>
<p>封装 BaiduMap 组件：</p>
<div class="language-html line-numbers-mode" data-ext="html"><pre v-pre class="language-html"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">:id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>bmapId<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">:style</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>{ width: '100%', height: '100%' }<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>
